{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762173361494","path":null,"data":{"id":1196,"title":"Manulife:推出新產品「守護無間危疾保系列」","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1658978395831,"tags":["宏利金融"],"content":"<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一、為滿足市場上對多重危疾保障日益增長的需求，<strong>Manulife宏利推出</strong>「<strong><span style=\"color: #169179;\">守護無間危疾保</span></strong>」及「<strong><span style=\"color: #169179;\">守護無間危疾保(保寶未來)</span></strong>」。涵蓋121種危疾，對癌症、心臟病、中風、認知障礙及柏金遜病甚至傷殘提供額外保障。3種額外癌症保障供客戶靈活選擇。更為孕婦及出生後的嬰孩提供周全保障。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #169179;\">守護無間危疾保系列</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #169179;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">亦將<strong>納入</strong>現有之<strong>歲稅樂享延期年金客戶推廣計劃</strong>及<strong>危疾定義更新計劃。</strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 於<strong><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">2022年7月25日至10月31日</span></strong>，成功申請<strong><span style=\"color: #169179;\">守護無間危疾保系列，</span><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">首2年合共可享高達30%</span></strong>的保費折扣優惠。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2022-07-28/d6a8065d4ee74a419d4f5e70698904b5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-f